libqbit-application-model-sendmail-perl (0.003) raring; urgency=low

  * Use hash_transform instead of one to one assigning.

  * Do not warn on empty headers.
  * Often and often fields cc, bcc and source_spot are empty. Indeed they
    have undef value. When new MIME object is created it warns about
    undefined value in string concatenation. This commit resolves the
    described problem.

